#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.calligra.braindump.metainfo.xml:11
msgid "Braindump"
msgstr "Braindump"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.calligra.braindump.metainfo.xml:12
msgid "Notes and ideas gathering"
msgstr "Notes et ensemble d'idées"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.calligra.braindump.metainfo.xml:14
msgid ""
"Braindump is a tool to dump and organize the content of your brain (ideas, "
"drawings, images, texts…) to your computer. It works by allowing to create "
"and edit whiteboards, which are infinite canvas on which you can add texts, "
"images, charts, drawings, etc."
msgstr ""
"Braindump est un outil pour mettre en ordre le contenu de votre cerveau "
"(idées, dessins, images, textes…) sur votre ordinateur. Il vous permet de "
"créer et d'éditer des tableaux blancs illimités sur lesquels vous pouvez "
"ajouter des textes, des images, des graphiques, des dessins, etc."

#. (itstool) path: screenshot/caption
#: org.kde.calligra.braindump.metainfo.xml:24
msgid ""
"Main window of Braindump showing a music partition and many other shapes"
msgstr ""
"Fenêtre principale de Braindump affichant une partition musicale et de "
"nombreuses autres formes"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.calligra.braindump.metainfo.xml:59
msgid "This release add flatpak support to the Calligra Office suite."
msgstr ""
"Cette version ajoute la prise en charge de FlatPak à la suite Calligra "
"Office."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.calligra.braindump.metainfo.xml:65
msgid ""
"The most significant changes are that Calligra has been fully transitioned "
"to Qt6 and KF6, along with a major overhaul of its user interface."
msgstr ""
"Les modifications les plus significatives sont que Calligra a été "
"entièrement migré vers Qt6 et KF6 et une refonte majeure de son interface "
"utilisateur."
